<p>使用 WAMPServer 时自定义网站根目录。</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="wampserver-自定义网站根目录">WAMPServer 自定义网站根目录</h2>
<h3 id="修改-apache-配置文件">修改 apache 配置文件</h3>
<p>打开<code>httpd.conf</code>文件搜索<code>documentroot</code>后，找到路径修改为自定义的。<br>
<a class="lightgallery" href="/posts/wamproot/images/httpd.png?size=large" data-thumbnail="/posts/wamproot/images/httpd.png?size=small" data-sub-html="<h2>修改 httpd.conf 文件</h2>"><img loading="lazy" src="/posts/wamproot/images/httpd.png" srcset="/posts/wamproot/images/httpd.png?size=small, /posts/wamproot/images/httpd.png?size=medium 1.5x, /posts/wamproot/images/httpd.png?size=large 2x" sizes="auto" data-title="修改 httpd.conf 文件" data-alt="修改 httpd.conf 文件" style="--width: 892px;--aspect-ratio: 892 / 309;background: url(/svg/loading.min.svg) no-repeat center;" onload="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}this.dataset.lazyloaded='';" onerror="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}"/></a></p>
<p>再打开<code>httpd-vhost.conf</code>文件修改对应的路径。<br>
<code>修改完配置文件需要重启所有服务！</code></p>
<h3 id="修改-wampmanager-文件">修改 wampmanager 文件</h3>
<p>在 wampserver 安装路径根目录知道<code>wampmanager.ini</code>和<code>wampmanager.tpl</code>两个文件。搜索<code>menu.left</code>, 然后也修改为自定义的路径。
<code>然后退出，重启软件！</code></p>
<p><a class="lightgallery" href="/posts/wamproot/images/wampmanager-ini.png?size=large" data-thumbnail="/posts/wamproot/images/wampmanager-ini.png?size=small" data-sub-html="<h2>修改 wampmanager.ini 文件</h2>"><img loading="lazy" src="/posts/wamproot/images/wampmanager-ini.png" srcset="/posts/wamproot/images/wampmanager-ini.png?size=small, /posts/wamproot/images/wampmanager-ini.png?size=medium 1.5x, /posts/wamproot/images/wampmanager-ini.png?size=large 2x" sizes="auto" data-title="修改 wampmanager.ini 文件" data-alt="修改 wampmanager.ini 文件" style="--width: 967px;--aspect-ratio: 967 / 415;background: url(/svg/loading.min.svg) no-repeat center;" onload="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}this.dataset.lazyloaded='';" onerror="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}"/></a><br>
<a class="lightgallery" href="/posts/wamproot/images/wampmanager-tpl.png?size=large" data-thumbnail="/posts/wamproot/images/wampmanager-tpl.png?size=small" data-sub-html="<h2>修改 wampmanager.tpl 文件</h2>"><img loading="lazy" src="/posts/wamproot/images/wampmanager-tpl.png" srcset="/posts/wamproot/images/wampmanager-tpl.png?size=small, /posts/wamproot/images/wampmanager-tpl.png?size=medium 1.5x, /posts/wamproot/images/wampmanager-tpl.png?size=large 2x" sizes="auto" data-title="修改 wampmanager.tpl 文件" data-alt="修改 wampmanager.tpl 文件" style="--width: 913px;--aspect-ratio: 913 / 380;background: url(/svg/loading.min.svg) no-repeat center;" onload="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}this.dataset.lazyloaded='';" onerror="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}"/></a></p>
