<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">$sudo hwclock --localtime --systohc</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p>重新进入 windows10，发现时间恢复正常了！</p>]]></description></item><item><title>windows 上搭建 web 服务器</title><link>https://lruihao.cn/posts/web-server-win/</link><pubDate>Fri, 26 Oct 2018 21:56:18 +0000</pubDate><author>Lruihao</author><guid>https://lruihao.cn/posts/web-server-win/</guid><description><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>我用的 win10</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="打开控制面板">打开控制面板</h3>
<p>选择并进入“程序”，双击“启用或关闭 Windows 服务”，在弹出的窗口中选择“Internet Information Services”下面所有地选项，点击确定后，开始更新服务。<br>
<figure><a class="lightgallery" href="/posts/web-server-win/images/1.png?size=large" data-thumbnail="/posts/web-server-win/images/1.png?size=small" data-sub-html="<h2>打开控制面板</h2><p>打开控制面板</p>"><img loading="lazy" src="/posts/web-server-win/images/1.png" srcset="/posts/web-server-win/images/1.png?size=small, /posts/web-server-win/images/1.png?size=medium 1.5x, /posts/web-server-win/images/1.png?size=large 2x" sizes="auto" data-title="打开控制面板" data-alt="打开控制面板" style="--width: 1408px;--aspect-ratio: 1408 / 742;background: url(/svg/loading.min.svg) no-repeat center;" onload="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}this.dataset.lazyloaded='';" onerror="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}"/></a><figcaption class="image-caption">打开控制面板</figcaption>
  </figure></p>
<h3 id="查看">查看</h3>
<p>更新完成后，打开浏览器，输入<code>http://localhost</code>或者<code>127.0.0.1</code>回车，如果此时出现 IIS7 欢迎界面，说明 Web 服务器已经搭建成功。<br>
<figure><a class="lightgallery" href="/posts/web-server-win/images/2.png?size=large" data-thumbnail="/posts/web-server-win/images/2.png?size=small" data-sub-html="<h2>查看</h2><p>查看</p>"><img loading="lazy" src="/posts/web-server-win/images/2.png" srcset="/posts/web-server-win/images/2.png?size=small, /posts/web-server-win/images/2.png?size=medium 1.5x, /posts/web-server-win/images/2.png?size=large 2x" sizes="auto" data-title="查看" data-alt="查看" style="--width: 1920px;--aspect-ratio: 1920 / 1030;background: url(/svg/loading.min.svg) no-repeat center;" onload="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}this.dataset.lazyloaded='';" onerror="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}"/></a><figcaption class="image-caption">查看</figcaption>
  </figure></p>
<h3 id="网站设置">网站设置</h3>
<p>当 web 服务器搭建成功后，我们下一步所要做的就是把我们开发的网站安装到 Web 服务器的目录中。一般情况下，当 Web 服务器安装完成后，会创建路径<code>%系统根目录%inetpub/wwwroot</code>，将我们开发的网站 COPY 到该路径下。即可实现本地访问该网站。<br>
<a class="lightgallery" href="/posts/web-server-win/images/3.png?size=large" data-thumbnail="/posts/web-server-win/images/3.png?size=small" data-sub-html="<h2>/posts/web-server-win/images/3.png</h2>"><img loading="lazy" src="/posts/web-server-win/images/3.png" srcset="/posts/web-server-win/images/3.png?size=small, /posts/web-server-win/images/3.png?size=medium 1.5x, /posts/web-server-win/images/3.png?size=large 2x" sizes="auto" data-title="/posts/web-server-win/images/3.png" data-alt="/posts/web-server-win/images/3.png" style="--width: 886px;--aspect-ratio: 886 / 239;background: url(/svg/loading.min.svg) no-repeat center;" onload="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}this.dataset.lazyloaded='';" onerror="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}"/></a></p>
<p>也可以更改根目录，搜索 IIS，点击网站，Default Web Site，基本设置修改物理路径（<strong>默认站点名称不要改</strong>）<br>
我这里改到了 hexo 的 public 相当于 hexo 部署在本地服务器<code>58.45.227.225</code><br>
<a class="lightgallery" href="/posts/web-server-win/images/5.png?size=large" data-thumbnail="/posts/web-server-win/images/5.png?size=small" data-sub-html="<h2>/posts/web-server-win/images/5.png</h2><p>网站设置 1</p>"><img loading="lazy" src="/posts/web-server-win/images/5.png" srcset="/posts/web-server-win/images/5.png?size=small, /posts/web-server-win/images/5.png?size=medium 1.5x, /posts/web-server-win/images/5.png?size=large 2x" sizes="auto" data-title="网站设置 1" data-alt="/posts/web-server-win/images/5.png" style="--width: 487px;--aspect-ratio: 487 / 854;background: url(/svg/loading.min.svg) no-repeat center;" onload="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}this.dataset.lazyloaded='';" onerror="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}"/></a>
<a class="lightgallery" href="/posts/web-server-win/images/6.png?size=large" data-thumbnail="/posts/web-server-win/images/6.png?size=small" data-sub-html="<h2>/posts/web-server-win/images/6.png</h2><p>网站设置 2</p>"><img loading="lazy" src="/posts/web-server-win/images/6.png" srcset="/posts/web-server-win/images/6.png?size=small, /posts/web-server-win/images/6.png?size=medium 1.5x, /posts/web-server-win/images/6.png?size=large 2x" sizes="auto" data-title="网站设置 2" data-alt="/posts/web-server-win/images/6.png" style="--width: 1156px;--aspect-ratio: 1156 / 619;background: url(/svg/loading.min.svg) no-repeat center;" onload="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}this.dataset.lazyloaded='';" onerror="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}"/></a>
<a class="lightgallery" href="/posts/web-server-win/images/7.png?size=large" data-thumbnail="/posts/web-server-win/images/7.png?size=small" data-sub-html="<h2>/posts/web-server-win/images/7.png</h2><p>网站设置 3</p>"><img loading="lazy" src="/posts/web-server-win/images/7.png" srcset="/posts/web-server-win/images/7.png?size=small, /posts/web-server-win/images/7.png?size=medium 1.5x, /posts/web-server-win/images/7.png?size=large 2x" sizes="auto" data-title="网站设置 3" data-alt="/posts/web-server-win/images/7.png" style="--width: 1920px;--aspect-ratio: 1920 / 1032;background: url(/svg/loading.min.svg) no-repeat center;" onload="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}this.dataset.lazyloaded='';" onerror="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}"/></a></p>
<h3 id="设置防火墙">设置防火墙</h3>
<p>让局域网当其它计算机也能访问本地网站资源。具体方法：打开控制面板，选择“系统和安全”，点击“允许程序通过 Windows 防火墙”，在弹出的对话框中勾选“万维网服务 HTTP”右侧的两个复选框，最后点击确定退出。<br>
<a class="lightgallery" href="/posts/web-server-win/images/4.png?size=large" data-thumbnail="/posts/web-server-win/images/4.png?size=small" data-sub-html="<h2>/posts/web-server-win/images/4.png</h2><p>设置防火墙</p>"><img loading="lazy" src="/posts/web-server-win/images/4.png" srcset="/posts/web-server-win/images/4.png?size=small, /posts/web-server-win/images/4.png?size=medium 1.5x, /posts/web-server-win/images/4.png?size=large 2x" sizes="auto" data-title="设置防火墙" data-alt="/posts/web-server-win/images/4.png" style="--width: 1408px;--aspect-ratio: 1408 / 742;background: url(/svg/loading.min.svg) no-repeat center;" onload="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}this.dataset.lazyloaded='';" onerror="this.title=this.dataset.title;this.alt=this.dataset.alt;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','data-alt','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}"/></a></p>
<p>在局域网中其它计算机上，打开浏览器就可以通过你电脑的 ip 地址访问了（手机也可以）<br>
本地 ip 可以通过 cmd 用 ipconfig 查看</p>
